OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will set out a "fresh
OL,8,Fdirection" as he battles to save his
OL,9,Fjob in the face of a leadership
OL,10,Fchallenge following Labour's
OL,11,Fdisastrous election results.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister, who has indicated
OL,14,Fhe hopes to remain in power until
OL,15,F2034, has a major speech on Monday as
OL,16,Fhe tries to shore up his position
OL,17,Fafter the MP Catherine West declared
OL,18,Fher intention to launch a leadership
OL,19,Fbid.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
