OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FFormer minister Ms West intends to
OL,8,Fseek nominations on Monday but has
OL,9,Fmade clear her campaign is an attempt
OL,10,Fto force the Cabinet to get behind a
OL,11,Fcandidate to move against Sir Keir
OL,12,Frather than a credible challenge to
OL,13,Fwin the keys to No 10 herself.
OL,15,FAs well as Monday's event, the King's
OL,16,FSpeech on Wednesday, setting out the
OL,17,Fgovernment's priorities, will form
OL,18,Fpart of an attempt by Sir Keir to
OL,19,Freset his leadership after Labour was
OL,20,Fhammered at the ballot box.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
