OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FIn a further blow, former loyalist
OL,8,FJosh Simons called for Sir Keir to
OL,9,Fquit, saying he had "lost the country".
OL,11,FDespite the mounting calls for him to
OL,12,Fleave, the Prime Minister said he
OL,13,Fwould not walk away from the job.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
