OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FAsked if he would lead Labour at the
OL,8,Fnext election, expected in 2029, and
OL,9,Fserve a full term of up to five years,
OL,10,Fhe told the Sunday Mirror: "Yes I
OL,11,Fwill, and I've always said it's a
OL,12,Fdecade of national renewal, where the
OL,13,Flegacy we inherited was an appalling
OL,14,Flegacy on all fronts, not just the
OL,15,Feconomy, which was broken."
OL,26,@rD@\OUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
