OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FSir Keir has been hit by Nigel
OL,8,FFarage's Reform UK snatching councils,
OL,9,Fsome of which had been Labour for
OL,10,Fgenerations, in northern England while
OL,11,FZack Polanski's Green Party lured
OL,12,Fvoters away from him in former urban
OL,13,Fstrongholds, including taking control
OL,14,Fof some London authorities.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FBut Sir Keir told the Observer: "I
OL,8,Fhave a strong belief that there aren't
OL,9,Fmany people who actually want Zack
OL,10,FPolanski or Nigel Farage as prime
OL,11,Fminister.
OL,13,F"I think that the mainstream majority
OL,14,Factually want to know that we, the
OL,15,Fgovernment, have progressive answers
OL,16,Fto the challenges that they face on a
OL,17,Fdaily basis, and we need to spell out
OL,18,Fin terms and with conviction that we
OL,19,Fdo have those progressive answers."
OL,26,@oD@aOUuD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
