CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,8,Fsaid people felt "bitterly let down"
OL,9,Fby Labour.
OL,11,F"I just do not believe that the
OL,12,Fmessage we should take from these
OL,13,Felections is that we ought to spend
OL,14,Ftime as a party amongst ourselves,
OL,15,Farguing amongst ourselves, fighting
OL,16,Famongst ourselves," she told the BBC.
OL,18,F"We do need to tell a better story. We
OL,19,Fdo need to deliver faster."
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@dO]sD@AOUxD@SO]zD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
