OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FShe added: "The Prime Minister will
OL,8,Fset out a fresh direction for our
OL,9,Fcountry and for our party that will
OL,10,Frise to the scale of what we face."
OL,12,FFormer junior minister Catherine West
OL,13,Fhas called on the cabinet to challenge
OL,14,FStarmer's leadership, or she shall do
OL,15,Fso herself
OL,17,FMs West said she would wait to hear
OL,18,FSir Keir's speech on Monday before
OL,19,Fbeginning the process of gathering the
OL,20,F81 MPs she would need to formally
OL,21,Ftrigger a contest.
OL,26,@oD@LOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
