CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FShe told BBC's Sunday With Laura
OL,8,FKuenssberg: "I will hear what the
OL,9,FPrime Minister's got to say tomorrow
OL,10,Fand, then if I'm still dissatisfied, I
OL,11,Fwill put out my email to the
OL,12,FParliamentary Labour Party, asking for
OL,13,Fnames.
OL,15,F"And the reason I'm doing that is not
OL,16,Ffor me.
OL,18,F"It's for working people, because
OL,19,FLabour is the only party that can beat
OL,20,FReform."
OL,26,@pD@MOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
