OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FShe added: "I say to the women of the
OL,8,FParliamentary Labour Party, don't just
OL,9,Fallow the men to stand."
OL,11,FFormer deputy leader Angela Rayner is
OL,12,Fwidely viewed as a potential
OL,13,Fleadership contender, with Health
OL,14,FSecretary Wes Streeting likely to be
OL,15,Fher main rival within the
OL,16,Fparliamentary party.
OL,26,@oD@LOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
