CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FBut Greater Manchester Mayor Andy
OL,8,FBurnham would need to fight and win a
OL,9,Fby-election to become an MP to further
OL,10,Fhis own leadership ambitions, meaning
OL,11,Fhis supporters are wary of a quick
OL,12,Fcontest to replace Sir Keir.
OL,14,FIn the latest sign that discontent
OL,15,Fwith the Prime Minister has gone
OL,16,Fbeyond the usual critics on the Labour
OL,17,Fleft, former minister Mr Simons called
OL,18,Ffor him to go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
