CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778501468
OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FThe Makerfield MP wrote in the Times:
OL,8,F"Putting the people I represent and
OL,9,Fthe country I love first, I do not
OL,10,Fbelieve the Prime Minister can rise to
OL,11,Fthis moment.
OL,13,F"He has lost the country.
OL,15,F"He should take control of the
OL,16,Fsituation by overseeing an orderly
OL,17,Ftransition to a new prime minister."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUwD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
