OL,3,CStarmer fighting to keep job as former
OL,4,Cminister warns he has 'lost the
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FJohn McDonnell, the former shadow
OL,8,Fchancellor under Jeremy Corbyn and a
OL,9,Fsenior figure on the Labour left,
OL,10,Furged Ms West to back down from
OL,11,Fpotentially triggering a quick contest
OL,12,For coronation for Sir Keir's successor.
OL,14,F"We need to discuss how we go
OL,15,Fforward," he said.
OL,17,F"I worry some in shadows want to
OL,18,Fexploit her concerns and bounce us
OL,19,Fbefore we have a proper democratic
OL,20,Fprocess."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@IO]yD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
